<h1>Password Reset</h1>

<p>To reset your password please click the link below:</p>

<%= link_to "Reset password", edit_forgot_password_url(@user.reset_token, email: @user.email) %>

<p>This link will expire in 2 hours.</p>

<p>If you did not request your password to be reset please ignore this email and your password will remain the same.</p>

<p>Thank you for using Helping Hand.</p>